data.description: BUYER CONCESSION AVAILABLE$$$ Own this home with three bedrooms and two bathrooms for the American Dream. Solid block/brick construction with approximately 1500 square feet under heat and air condition. 2204 total square footage. Priced to sell and ready for you to move in. Centrally located in the 1st area of Deltona, the biggest city in Volusia County. Close to Interstate I-4 and 30 minutes to Orlando and World-famous Daytona Beach. This home has a Fenced in back yard, (10x12) a screen porch and a (17x12) Florida room which could be a fourth bedroom or just for sleep overs. Kitchen appliances are approx. one year old and a washer & dryer in the garage with lots of storage. Master bedroom has a walk-in closet and master bath has a walk-in shower. Quiet community and a spring fed large lake across the street.  Call today, don't delay!  Can Be Yours!
